'''诗人公馆'''（Hôtel du Poët）是法国[[普罗旺斯地区艾克斯|普罗旺斯地区艾克斯]]的一座宅邸。

==位置==
它位于普罗旺斯地区艾克斯的[[米拉波大道|米拉波大道]]起点的福尔班广场（Place Forbin）<ref name="tourism">{{Cite web |url=http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-hp-mirabeau.htm |title=Aix-en-Provence Tourism: Hôtels particuliers à Aix en Provence |access-date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215130346/http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-hp-mirabeau.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="tourismcours">{{Cite web |url=http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-cours.htm |title=Aix-en-Provence Tourism: Cours Mirabeau |access-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102205834/http://www.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-cours.htm |archive-date=2013-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="culture13">{{Cite web |url=http://www.culture-13.fr/annuaire/hotel-du-poet.html |title=Culture 13: Hôtel du Poet |access-date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218114911/http://www.culture-13.fr/annuaire/hotel-du-poet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Fernand Chabaud, ''Aix-en-Provence: guide du touriste'', F. Detaille, 1946, p. 11 [https://books.google.com/books?id=4r7TAAAAMAAJ&q=%22H%C3%B4tel+du+Po%C3%ABt%22+aix&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+du+Po%C3%ABt%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=RRCtUo2sK8urhQeOqoHoBQ&ved=0CFwQ6AEwAjgK]</ref>

==历史==
1730年，亨利·高蒂埃（1676-1757年）在米拉波大道起点购买了一些土地，那里有一个古老的[[水磨|水磨]]。<ref name="tourism"/><ref name="tourismcours"/><ref name="culture13"/><ref name="ambroise">Ambroise Roux-Alphéran, ''Les rues d'Aix: ou, Recherches historiques sur l'ancienne capitale de la Provence'', Aubin, 1848, Volume 2, pp. 169-172 [https://books.google.com/books?id=ZVlGAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA170&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+du+Po%C3%ABt%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=oA6tUpGYBI2p7AbFuoGoDw&ved=0CGkQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=%22H%C3%B4tel%20du%20Po%C3%ABt%22%20aix&f=false]</ref><ref name="boyer">Jean Boyer, ''Architecture et urbanisme à Aix-en-Provence aux XVIIe-XVIIIe siècles: du cours à carrosses au cours Mirabeau'', Ville d'Aix-en-Provence, 2004, p. 87-88 [https://books.google.com/books?id=GG5IAQAAIAAJ&q=%22henri+gautier%22+aix&dq=%22henri+gautier%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=8SmtUu78C4uS7Abn3IA4&ved=0CIIBEOgBMAk4Cg]</ref> 他委托建筑师乔治·瓦隆（Georges Vallon，1688-1767 年）设计了一座宅邸：诗人公馆。<ref name="tourism"/><ref name="tourismcours"/><ref name="culture13"/><ref name="boyer"/> 后来，这里是药剂师和印刷厂的所在地。<ref name="ambroise"/>

这是一座[[巴洛克建筑|巴洛克建筑]]<ref name="culture13"/>。立面有怪面饰<ref>Dominique Auzias, ''Aix-en-Provence'', Le Petit Futé, 2008, p. 144 [https://books.google.com/books?id=QuMgNOGgBncC&pg=PA144&dq=%22H%C3%B4tel+du+Po%C3%ABt%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=oA6tUpGYBI2p7AbFuoGoDw&ved=0CEYQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22H%C3%B4tel%20du%20Po%C3%ABt%22%20aix&f=false]</ref> 室内主楼梯有圆柱，路易十六扶手装饰有诗人饰牌<ref name="tourism"/>。

==保护==
自1987年11月3日以来，它被列为[[法国历史遗迹|法国历史遗迹]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/public/mistral/merimee_fr?ACTION=CHERCHER&FIELD_1=REF&VALUE_1=PA00081047 |title=French Ministry of Culture |access-date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2019-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019000308/http://www2.culture.gouv.fr/public/mistral/merimee_fr%3FACTION%3DCHERCHER%26FIELD_1%3DREF%26VALUE_1%3DPA00081047 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

